data.description:
Welcome to this gorgeous, Pulte home with a 3-car garage, luxurious upgrades, and located in the desirable Festival Foothills community! Fully owned solar panels for an energy efficient home! Sitting on a premium corner on over 13,000sqft, this 3 bedroom+office  2-bathroom home will not disappoint! The great room floorplan is well-thought-out with no wasted space! The kitchen is beautiful with exquisite upgrades, granite countertops, white 42'' cabinets with crown molding, stainless steel wall appliances, a gas cook top, a walk-in pantry, and a large kitchen island with a breakfast bar. The primary suite is spacious with a lavish ensuite bathroom featuring a tiled walk-in shower, a dual sink vanity, and a walk-in closet. Bedrooms 2 and 3 are move in ready and complete with recessed canned lighting. The office off the foyer has a double glass door entry. The backyard is expansive with a covered patio with a ceiling fan and an extended paved seating area. Plus, an RV gate! This home is spotless and move-in ready, do not miss your opportunity to see this home.
 
Festival Foothills is a serene community with amenities such as a splash pad, playgrounds, and walking paths. Buckeye Az is a growing area that is close to regional parks, aquatic centers, golf, and much more! Do not miss out on this stunning home!
